  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Welcome to Bravo Motel, where one cleaning shift unleashes a nightmare told through <strong>two perspectives</strong>. Begin as <strong><i>Allison</i></strong>, a woman seeking refuge from her past, only to find yourself entangled in the motel's sinister web. Then step into <strong><i>Emma</i></strong>'s shoes, where what seemed like a desperate bid for safety becomes a horrifying revelation. As you experience the same events through different eyes, the true nature of Bravo Motel's terror begins to surface, challenging everything you thought you knew.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><i>🎭 DUAL PERSPECTIVE NARRATIVE</i></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Experience the story through two intertwined characters</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Uncover shocking revelations as perspectives shift</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Watch as two timelines collide to reveal the haunting truth</p></li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><i>🧹 IMMERSIVE CLEANING SIMULATOR</i></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Fully interactive environment with realistic physics</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Detailed cleaning animations that make every task satisfying</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Master the art of housekeeping while uncovering clues</p></li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><i>🔍 MIND-BENDING MYSTERY</i></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Piece together a narrative that challenges perception</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >See how one event can have two terrifying interpretations</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Unravel the truth behind Bravo Motel's sinister facade </p></li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><i>👻 PSYCHOLOGICAL HORROR</i></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Photorealistic graphics that blur the line between game and reality</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Atmospheric tension that builds with each discovered secret</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Environmental storytelling that keeps you questioning reality</p></li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>🎮 Join Our Community Discord! 🌟</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Experiencing issues in the game? Need support or want to provide feedback? Our Discord is the place to be!</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >🚨 <strong>Instant Support Guaranteed</strong> 🚨</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Report bugs directly to the developers</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Get real-time updates and patches</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Connect with other players</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Immediate attention to your concerns</p></li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><u><i><br></i></u></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3187540/extras/cc71aa1645d40659de56e17a7cec8a24.poster.avif?t=1734090727\" width=616 height=346 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3187540/extras/cc71aa1645d40659de56e17a7cec8a24.webm?t=1734090727\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3187540/extras/cc71aa1645d40659de56e17a7cec8a24.mp4?t=1734090727\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3187540/extras/5c201d5be9923d8976e5bb8f839f5f46.poster.avif?t=1734090727\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3187540/extras/5c201d5be9923d8976e5bb8f839f5f46.webm?t=1734090727\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3187540/extras/5c201d5be9923d8976e5bb8f839